data.description: Awaiting a New Owner!! This Well-loved 3-bedroom 2 bath attached home (1791sqft) in Brookshire Retreat is ready for occupancy. It has an open floor plan, an oversized Master Suite with a gorgeous view. The master bath includes double vanities, a separate tiled shower along with a large, jetted tub. The kitchen is equipped with numerous cabinets, stainless appliances, granite countertops, a beautiful custom backsplash and a large pantry. There wood and tiled floors throughout the home. This home has a separate laundry room. The screened back porch enclosure overlooks beautiful water/fountain view. Brookshire Retreat is one of the subdivisions in Laurel Island, a public golf course community.
